msgid "Zipper.16"
msgstr "Zipper.16"

#: addons/Zipper_16.wad/dirnames:4 input:4 standard
msgid "Add-On Maps"
msgstr "Add-On Kaarten"

#: input:6 standard
msgid ""
"Can 16 players fit into a world like that? Find out—you'll have to come out "
"on top against 15 others! <br> <br>Version 2.00"
msgstr ""
"Passen er wel 16 spelers in zo’n wereld? Ontdek het zelf—je moet je tegen 15 "
"anderen zien te handhaven! <br> <br>Versie 2.00"

#: input:7 input:13 standard
msgid "Yellow and purple, blue and white, orange and green, red and black."
msgstr "Geel en paars, blauw en wit, oranje en groen, rood en zwart."
